  "title": "Sales Consulant",
  "description": "<p>Hayashi is a leading supplier of premium <strong>engineered and composite wood flooring solutions</strong>, serving both retail customers and corporate clients including interior design firms, architects, developers, and main contractors. Our commitment to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction has made us a trusted partner in the flooring industry.</p>\n<p>As we continue to grow, we are looking for a dynamic and driven <strong>Sales Consultant</strong> to join our team and take our business to the next level.</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Sales &amp; Account Management<br>\n- </strong>Proactively identify and develop new business opportunities across both <strong>retail</strong> and <strong>corporate segments</strong>.<br>\n- Build and maintain strong relationships with <strong>interior designers, architects, developers, contractors</strong>, and direct consumers.<br>\n- Handle incoming leads and convert them into successful sales.</li>\n  <li><strong>Client Consultation<br>\n- </strong>Understand client needs and recommend suitable flooring solutions.<br>\n- Provide product demonstrations and samples, and prepare customized quotations.<br>\n- Offer expert advice on product selection, installation requirements, and after-sales care.</li>\n  <li><strong>Project Coordination<br>\n- </strong>Collaborate with internal teams and external stakeholders to ensure timely delivery and project execution.<br>\n- Follow up on project timelines, payments, and customer satisfaction.</li>\n  <li><strong>Market Development<br>\n- </strong>Attend industry trade shows, exhibitions, and networking events to promote the brand.<br>\n- Keep abreast of market trends, competitor activity, and customer preferences.<br>\n- Provide feedback to management on market insights and opportunities.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Excellent communication, negotiation, and presentation skills.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in <strong>English and Chinese</strong></li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, target-driven, and comfortable working independently.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Base salary ($2,000) + attractive commission structure (up to $5-8K per month)</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for growth and advancement within a fast-growing company.</li>\n  <li>Supportive and collaborative work environment.</li>\n  <li>Product and sales training provided.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3>\n<p>Please send your resume and to <strong>javier@hayashi.sg</strong>, with the subject line:<br>\n<strong>\"Application – Sales Consultant\"</strong></p>",
